# BloomFree Terminal — Build Walkthrough

A fully functional Bloomberg-style financial dashboard built with pure HTML, CSS, and Chart.js — no backend, no subscription, 100% free.

## What Was Built

Three files in `C:\Users\Shree\Downloads\bloomberg\`:

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `index.html` | Full multi-panel dashboard layout with 5 views |
| `style.css` | Bloomberg dark theme — amber/green/red palette, JetBrains Mono font |
| `app.js` | Live price simulation engine, Chart.js charts, all panel data |

## Features Verified ✅

### Dashboard (F1)
- **Live scrolling ticker** at the top with real-time-style price updates
- **8 Market Indices** strip — S&P 500, NASDAQ, DOW, VIX, BTC, Gold, Crude Oil, USD Index
- **Watchlist** — 12 stocks (AAPL, MSFT, NVDA, GOOGL, AMZN, META, TSLA, JPM, V, JNJ, WMT, BAC) with live price simulation every 2 seconds, sparklines
- **Live Price Chart** — green/red line chart with Open/High/Low/Prev stats bar, 1D/1W/1M/3M timeframes
- **Top Movers** — Gainers & Losers ranked panels
- **Options Chain** — Calls & Puts table with Strike, Bid, Ask, IV, OI
- **Economic Calendar** — HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW impact events
- **News Feed** — BULLISH/BEARISH tagged headlines

### Charts View (F2)
- Full-screen expanded chart for deeper analysis

### Portfolio (F3)
- Holdings table with P&L, Market Value, Weight
- Doughnut allocation chart
- Summary stats: Total Value, Day P&L, Total P&L, Beta, Sharpe

### Crypto (F4)
- Full crypto market table (BTC, ETH, SOL, BNB, XRP, DOGE, ADA, AVAX)
- Fear & Greed Index gauge (72 — GREED)
- Market Dominance bar chart

### FX (F5)
- 12 currency pairs (EUR/USD, GBP/USD, USD/JPY, USD/INR, etc.)
- Live rate simulation with direction bars

